reviewText:
I am quite happy with the DVD.

I wish this DVD contained other medal winners' great performances, for example Lu Chen's performance was memorable and beautiful, but is not shown in this dvd even though she won a bronze medal...

But it was good to see Tara Lipinski's and other great skaters' performances!
I am sorry for evaluation to have become slow. Goods arrived safely. I am very much satisfied. Thank you very much.
